      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the screw-rod assembly. Construct stiffness changed by 1.4% and yield force by 1.1% between medium and fine meshes. Production mesh selected at medium refinement level as converged solution."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
