      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments by a second analyst.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by a second FEA engineer not involved in original construction. Boundary condition application, contact pair definitions, and material property assignments verified against design drawings and test protocol. No discrepancies identified."
