      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the identical implant geometry, material, and test configuration as specified in the COU. ASTM F1717 bench test protocol directly mirrors the regulatory submission test requirement. Validation domain is coincident with the COU domain for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm design."
    }
